(Definition)

Say it:

What do you want to change or improve?

Discovery

Where am I at?

  • What's working well?
  • What's making it work?
  • Why is it working?
  • What do you value?

Delivery

So, what do I need to do?

  • How can you...
  • make it happen?
  • sustainable?
  • overcome barriers?
  • Think SMART - specific, measurable, achievable, realistic, timely
  • Evaluate and re-do

Design

How can I get there?

  • What are your ideas to achieve your dream?
  • What ideas do you have to make your dream real?
  • How could you make the best idea's work?
  • Which ideas do you want to build on?
  • Think about the possibilities, implications, benefits, risks and rationale.

Dream

Where do I need to be?

  • What's the ideal future?
  • What's your ideal future?
  • What does this look like?
